Description:
SOMETHING SPECIAL IN A PRIME LOCATION
A lifestyle of complete luxury, comfort and space is assured to the occupant of this stunning home. Boasting a simple yet practical open floor plan, this well designed 29.8sq (approx.) home features a smooth integration between the stunning kitchen domain through to family meals area and decked alfresco entertaining space giving the home a free flowing feel. The gourmet kitchen features a massive 4 metre stone island bench, ample cupboard space, 900mm oven and impressive walk in pantry.
Sleeping quarters consists of large robed bedrooms master with huge dressing room and luxurious ensuite with double vanity. Additional bedrooms are well zoned and feature built in robes and are effortlessly complemented by the study area and sparkling centralised bathroom. To the rear of the home you will find a spacious theatre room which could be converted to a possible fourth bedroom or kids retreat.
Situated in a prime location and only walking distance Newbury Community Centre, Newbury Kindergarten, Newbury Primary School, Highlands Shopping Centre, Pelican Child Care, convenience stores, childrens parklands and much more.
Other features include: 900mm oven, ducted heating, 7 kilowatt split system, Hybrid flooring with built in underlay (25 year waterproof warranty), double blinds in bedrooms, drive through access, roller shutters, 5kws of solar, 2 and half car garage,
Please Note
We have obtained all information in this document from sources we believe to be reliable; however, we cannot guarantee its accuracy. Prospective buyers are advised to carry out their own investigations.

Description:
Outstanding Quality Home in Prime Location
Universal Real Estate Vic proudly presents this architecturally striking, this Henley -built polished home is a true blend of Modern Provincial charm, fused to delight the most fastidious of home purchasers looking for that warm homely feel. Well equipped with all the bells and whistles to impress first home buyers or even the savviest of Investors.
SPECIFICATIONS:
- BEDROOMS: 4 Spacious Bedrooms (Master Bedroom with Walk in Robe, Full Ensuite with Double Vanity, Double spaced tiled Shower and Direct access to backyard, other 3 Bedrooms with mirrored BIR and serviced by a central bathroom with bath tub.
- KITCHEN: Spacious Open Plan Living/ Dining Kitchen with 900 mm Stainless Steel Appliances with Gas Cooktop and Oven, Stone Benchtops, Double Fridge Space with Plumbing Connection, Glass Splashback and Walking Pantry with Glass framed Door,
- LIVING AREA: Open Plan Living Area with Designer Lights and downlights .
- HEAT/COOL: Ducted Heating.
- LAUNDRY: Spacious Laundry.
- PARKING: Double Car Garage with remote control access and Internal access.
- BACKYARD: Low Maintenance Backyard with Lush Green Grass and concreted sides .
- ADDITIONAL INCLUSIONS: Downlights, Quality Laminated Floor Boards, Linen Cupboard, Designer Customised Blinds and much more....
SCHOOLS:
-Aitken Creek Primary School ....0.31km
-Newbury Primary School..........1.13km
-Mount Ridley P-12 School........1.68Km
-Willmott Park Primary School....1.97km
- LOCATION:
Very Close to Craigieburn Central, Craigieburn Junction, Splash Craigieburn, Craigieburn Library, Hume Tennis and Community Centre, Watermill Reserve, Thorngrove Reserve, Medical Centre and easy access to Hume Freeway.
The Property is currently tenanted for $1864 per Month and Tenanted till 04/01/2020.
If you're in the market for that perfect all round property, then look no further than this.
Don't miss out! Call Achal Arora - 0432 413 929 or Robbie Sandhu - 0466 074 588.

Brand New - Superb Placement & Style!
Be quick to inspect this charming brand new family home offering gorgeous street appeal with loads of character and style, perfect for first home-buyers and investors alike.
This beautiful home comes equipped with luxury turn-key inclusions such stone bench tops, carpets, tiles, high ceilings, alarm system and much more. Front landscaping, driveway and quality flooring are also all included in this beautiful home.
- 4 spacious bedrooms, master with full double vanity ensuite and walk in robe, additional 3 bedrooms all with built in robes.
- Well-equipped kitchen & stainless steel cooking appliances including 900 mm gas cook top, range hood, dishwasher, walk in pantry and island bench.
- Open plan living space comprising spacious dining and living area
- Modern central bathroom
- Spacious laundry
- Central ducted heating and provision for evaporative cooling
- Concrete perimeter around the house and security alarm
Complete with a remote car garage, private alfresco & good size backyard for the kids to enjoy and much more. Perfectly positioned close to Highlands Shopping Centre, popular schools, public transport, parks and sporting facilities. Inspection is a must!

Description:
Modern & Spacious Family Entertainer !
Stamp Duty saver with luxury Design!!! $10,000 FHOG for eligible buyers!!
Mike Sarupria & Ray White Tarneit presents Porter Davis built beauty in the prestigious The Hinghlands Estate.
(Please use Apple maps or www.whereis.com to navigate the property)
With it's own shopping precinct on the way, park-lands and open spaces, sports grounds, and two proposed schools in walking distance, it has something for every family.
24 Paprika Way Tarneit offers a sense of luxury as well as lifestyle options thanks to its practical floor-plan and good use of space. This single-level home is designed with couples and young families in mind "who want to start without compromise and have room to grow".
With 4 bedrooms and a spacious formal lounge, the formal lounge is well positioned at the front of the home to welcome people into the home or as a secluded place to enjoy downtime away from the home's main-living hub.
The family room is a dominant feature in the house - intimate, yet spacious and open and doused in natural light.
The kitchen also features a handy servery to the alfresco area, ensuring the living area is geared to year-round entertaining. It also has a walk-in pantry for convenient extra storage space.
24 Paprika Way features 4 bedrooms with master bedroom boasting a good size walk-in-robe and double vanity ensuite. Remaining 3 bedrooms comes with mirrored built in robes serviced by a central bathroom.
Inspired features are everywhere:
- Ducted heating & cooling - making you feel comfortable all around the year
- Fully landscaped front & backyard
- 900 mm stainless steel gas cook top and range- hood
- 20 mm stone benchtop in kitchen and bathrooms
- Remote control double lock garage
- Security alarm system and much more!!
Ray White Tarneit welcomes you and looks forward to meet you at the open homes.
Call Mike on 0430 126 491 or Frank on 0426 425 361 today to set an appointment for private inspection!!
(PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTION)

Description:
PREMIUM LOCATION, EASY LIVING
This stylish double storey has everything you would expect in a family home. With a great sense of space and light, the search may well be over. Entertaining will be made easy with living areas at the front and rear of the property with an opening on to a pergola area.
With walking distance to Mother Teresa Catholic Primary School and Olrig Field, this home is perfectly positioned for young families and investors. While its easy access to Public Transport, Highlands Shopping Centre and major arterials including the Grand Blvd and Hume Freeway makes life easy for all.
Other highlights include a well-appointed kitchen with stainless steel cooking appliances, ample cupboards, storage, dishwasher, ducted gas heating, Spa, 2 x powerful split air-conditioning systems on ground floor, Evaporative cooling on the First floor, CCTV security, garage with internal entry, low maintenance backyard and beautifully landscaped front, It surely ticks all the boxes.
This beautiful double storey house comes with 5 Bedrooms, Master with Ensuite, BIR, 3 Toilets, SPA, 3 Living areas, Enclosed Pergola, Rear Balcony and heaps of storage space. Inspection is must - contact Sumit today!
Sealed Bid Date: Monday 23rd September 2019 at 6.00pm.

Description:
Luxurious & Convenient Living!
Situated in the Highlands Estate is the perfect balance of space, style and convenience sure to impress all. This radiant three bedroom with no body corporate delivers smart low maintenance living with swift access to key lifestyle assets.
This remarkable residence features a functional floorplan inclusive of a spacious separate formal lounge, downstairs powder room, a sun soaked open plan living/meals area, kitchen area offering stainless steel appliances and Miele dishwasher. Adding to this comfortable floorplan is three generously sized bedrooms with built in robes, master equipped with walk in robe and oversized ensuite, glowing central bathroom with shower & separate bath.
Enhancing this property's indisputable appeal is ducted heating and split system cooling, electric roller shutters to all front facing windows, quality bamboo flooring, stylish light fittings, elegant ceiling to floor curtains in addition to the roller blinds, low maintenance backyard and double remote garage.
In a prime location close to all of Craigieburn's amenities, this property is surrounded by parks, within walking distance to Public Transport, Highlands-Stockland Shopping Centre, Mt Ridley College & Newbury Primary School. Be quick to inspect as this won't hang around for long.
